price: 74. With whom no man or jinni has had tamth[2] before them.
arabic: لَمۡ يَطۡمِثۡهُنَّ إِنسٞ قَبۡلَهُمۡ وَلَا جَآنّٞ
footnotes: (V.55:74) Tamth means: Opening their hymens with sexual intercourse.
